title.narrative: Bolivia Land for Agricultural Development Project.

description.narrative: The development objective of the proposed project is to establish a decentralized beneficiary-driven land distribution mechanism that allows organized landless or poor farmers to acquire suitable agricultural lands and implement investment subprojects which puts them on a sustainable, higher-income, livelihood path.
